   "text": "中国越来越重视公共图书馆，并鼓励人们充分加以利用。新近公布的统计数字表明，中国的公共图书馆数量在 逐年增长。许多图书馆通过翻新和扩建，为读者创造了更为安静、舒适的环境。大型公共图书馆不仅提供种类繁多 的参考资料，而且定期举办讲座、展览等活动。近年来，也出现了许多数字图书馆，从而节省了存放图书所需的空 间。一些图书馆还推出了自助服务系统，使读者借书还书更加方便，进一步满足了读者的需求。",
   "reference": "China is paying increasing attention to public libraries and encourages people to make full use of them. Recently released statistics show that the number of public libraries in China has been increasing year by year. Many libraries have created a quieter and more comfortable environment for readers through renovation and expansion. Large public libraries not only provide a wide variety of reference materials but also regularly hold lectures, exhibitions, and other events. In recent years, many digital libraries have emerged, thus saving the space needed for storing books. Some libraries have also introduced self-service systems, making it more convenient for readers to borrow and return books, and further meeting the needs of readers.",
